summary:
Author, editor, traveller. Passionate about people, hiking & nature.

An international upbringing in five countries and speaking seven languages, travel is a crucial part of my life. I flow between different cultures, building connections and friendships with people easily, in part due to my curiosity about people and their stories. 

I've creatively expressed these pieces of my life through two published books: "On My Way: 800 Kilometres to Destination Self"(2021), and "Being Human: Create Life By Your Own Design" (2022). 

I am currently enrolled in a part-time MA in Creative Writing (Hull University, Online), as well as a Freelance and Travel Journalism course (London School of Journalism). These are the next steps in enhancing my writing. Growth, whether professional or personal, is an endless journey that I am actively participating in.
